\description{
An \link[R6:R6Class]{R6} class that configures resampling-based support
analyses in \pkg{nitro}.

\code{ResamplingCommand} handles bootstrap, jackknife, and symmetric
resampling analyses through a single unified interface. The resampling
method is selected via the \verb{$method} field. This wraps the TNT
\code{resample} command.

The recommended way to create and attach a \code{ResamplingCommand} to a
\link{TreeAnalysis} is via \code{\link[=set_support]{set_support()}}.
}
