   Symmetric resampling \tab \code{"symmetric"} \tab Change probability (default: \code{36}). \cr
}


Setting \verb{$method} to \code{"bootstrap"} automatically clears \verb{$probability}.
Setting it to \code{"jackknife"} or \code{"symmetric"} sets \verb{$probability} to
\code{36} if not already specified.
}

